 />\n個陣中三著緊校服 嗰個情境個種感覺到宜家都勁深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72dab51d069b04f876787b165eb65de9768f716","tid":357794,"uid":51111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:57:21.000Z","msg":"今個星期差唔多日日都係街喊，其實真係唔想，但係忍唔撚到，佢係禁湧出尼屌"},{"pid":"08895596b5243adc028585e748b49257acdfeb6c","tid":357794,"uid":91082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:03:28.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上車喊到落車，轉車繼續喊。。。。全程係咁比人望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df999817b95ad582f069f17d13ca97b2527e6d2e","tid":357794,"uid":15960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:01:31.000Z","msg":"有 同ex鬧交 一路係個商場行一路係佢身後喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  啲人就一路喊 諗起都覺醜"},{"pid":"29dec8c56f56bc681d86ff8d8e44949402ed03f6","tid":357794,"uid":15960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有 同ex鬧交 一路係個商場行一路係佢身後喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  啲人就一路望 諗起都覺醜</blockquote>"},{"pid":"736cb71644f2e9d6fa6fe70477f5291ce4222ecd","tid":357794,"uid":130308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:35:26.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽到話要分手 佢同左第個一齊 係街爆喊<br />\n求其搵張櫈坐底喊到死<br />\n之後keep住一段時間 去到邊 食飯乜都好都眼濕濕<br />\n忍住唔流落嚟 <br />\n一開頭係傷心喊 過左排係嬲到喊 點解可以咁對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb5e93715b89c7b588b5b47f2818c4bd8802138","tid":357794,"uid":107605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"有  亦都識幾個朋友試過<br />\n有次我打比個朋友 就黎忍唔住<br />\n佢用好soft既語氣 好有經驗咁話<br />\n「冇事，深呼吸，dup低頭。」<br />\n<br />\n嗰刻對於佢充滿喺街喊經驗呢件事 鄧佢心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae95f1c810bc8d691975bfbd889b3e592675d4c","tid":357